{"about_the_game":"&quot;Proceed with extreme caution. Many dangers might be ahead. These include: creatures, demons, anomalies, ghosts, ancients, beasts, aliens, curses, malfunctions, ascendants, diseases, darkness and death. Your task is to find the smiling pictures. Desmile them. You will not be let back in until your task is complete. Begin.&quot;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSMILE SIMULATION is a surreal horror game where you are closed in a dangerous environment, with many rooms and corridors, as well as monsters and curses trying to kill you. Find the pictures on the walls that are smiling, the &quot;Desmile&quot; button turns them back to normal.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou'll find the previous explorer's voice logs - Brian was here some time ago, when the simulation appeared in the Lacrimosa facility. The Smile Simulation appears to have a voice of a woman named Vivian too, who's guiding you, but you're not sure where just yet.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nExplore the horrors of this place, find the smiling pictures, avoid the creatures that each behave in a unique way, the game also features a blinking mechanic that elevates the tension as it affects the creatures following you, and find out the secrets and the story surrounding this threatening place.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Smile Simulation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017250/e05a29996390cc2f9d5eb9be117ae1cae87d4897.jpg"},{"name":"Nightmare","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017250/a9338bfc8ecabd1171f51ee381f7f6c141a22f47.jpg"},{"name":"3 Mannequins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017250/3c0c6dfc6059a7c6e409e24b8594ab0231132137.jpg"},{"name":"Deadly Smiles","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017250/194dce750ab13862faed594c05c58a984d5a44c5.jpg"}],"total":4},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/